ygData.messageBody:
I am a high elf paladin and am wondering about some quests in my area.

1. The first quest I got was the "go to kelethin and talk to the drunk"
quest but I stoped because I have head that this is a broken quest and no on
who has finished it has gotten anything from it, is it broken, is it worth
doing.

2. The quest I have now is to Travel to the innothule swamp and kill the
Jojongua. I have not been able to find any info on this beast or any paladin
who has done this quest.. The guild master describes the Jojongua as a beast
of unbridled fury (or something like that) so it kinda scares me I am level
8 and don't want to track 1/2 accross the world to get my but kicked, does
anyone know what level is a good level for this quest and anymore info you
can give me on it would be great.

3. Ogre head... I killed Corflunk in BB and got the Ogre head it's a quest
item but is it for a Paladin quest? should I hold onto it or sell it to
someone who can use it.

Thanks


--
